Rating: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️☆ (4.5/5)
Verdict: &ldquo;The card system and dragon lore shine, but uneven pacing holds it back from perfection.&rdquo;
📖 Summary Story starts with seeking another card for Brixby’s legendary deck. For searching this new card, our group travelled to another hive (Blood Moon Hive) in the kingdom (let’s not forget they’re currently outside the kingdom). They found an illusion card to show their ranks one rank lower (legendary → rare, rare → uncommon) and infiltrate Blood Moon Hive to find the card.
